{"tid":423608,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬些路涉逃稅40萬歐元","createTime":"2017-10-04T04:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T06:05:17.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0642cd337318675a7a5ed26a4e745004b8507a","tid":423608,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"西班牙搵食的球星逐一被查，皇家馬德里左閘馬些路成為西班牙稅局的新目標，涉嫌逃稅40萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《世界報》披露，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>29歲巴西後衛馬些路（Marcelo）目前被西班牙稅局入稟馬德里地方法院，要求補交2013年的40萬歐元欠稅。</strong></span></span>皇馬主力馬些路被指4年前在肖像權收入上逃稅，款項達到40萬歐元，檢察官目前仍未決定會否起訴。 2015年，馬些路已補交部份欠稅，但西班牙稅局突然「舊事重提」，重新調查有關收入和稅收。 29歲的馬些路自從2007年加盟皇馬至今，一直擔任防線主力，期間贏過4次西甲、3次歐聯和2次西班牙盃冠軍，今年9月簽下新約直至2022年，而他是球隊4隊長的其中一位。"},{"pid":"ecfa12989595cdc3e7bfb94100e30288e6193fb8","tid":423608,"uid":4586,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"賤種蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be09be6e9c5ad0924067eb75cc7815b71f5ccdef","tid":423608,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賤種蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你牙"},{"pid":"4c78a55adf75052046af10a8da0b2d1404654247","tid":423608,"uid":14075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"咁既樣都有肖象權要交40萬稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6568b4c732139570e18bf6255f3fac3347effa9","tid":423608,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"要g持加泰獨立了 西班牙政府吸血鬼"},{"pid":"26e0570421f19dcd38bb0ca775af62e54cdc1ff9","tid":423608,"uid":35351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"黎追數喔"},{"pid":"4de39c8188d50000efa61935126e568a246f255c","tid":423608,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1